        "collapsible_row_NdV3hr": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Damages",
            "row_content": "<p>We pack every order with care, however, please check your order immediately after arrival to ensure no damage has occurred to the item (apart from normal wear expected to the outer packaging during shipment). If you believe the product has been tampered with or damaged, email us at <a href=\"mailto:care@loveindus.com\" title=\"mailto:care@loveindus.com\">care@loveindus.com</a> promptly with the issue and supporting photographs and order/ product details. Please retain the original shipping box, packaging materials (carton etc.) so these can be referenced during inspection by the shipping company/ courier service.</p>",
